com.application.skill_level

Interface SkillLevelRepository

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.springframework.data.repository.CrudRepository<SkillLevel,java.lang.Long>, org.springframework.data.repository.Repository<SkillLevel,java.lang.Long>

    @Repository
public interface SkillLevelRepository
extends org.springframework.data.repository.CrudRepository<SkillLevel,java.lang.Long>
    Interface extension of a CrudRepository to be a repository for SkillLevels. Implementation provided automatically by Hibernate.
    Author:
    Tim Schommer
